{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-00208/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-00208"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:02:08"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["high key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A woman opens the shutters on a floor-to-ceiling window."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-00208","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-00208"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/canvas/1/681bf66d-28ac-4b39-8556-c12503549c41","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:21:11.241Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Cyril, Reynolds’s sister, is first seen opening the window shutters. Deeply protective of her brother and their business, she is far from interested in “opening up” the House of Woodcock, but these shots demonstrate who truly runs the house. Her dark clothing makes her stand out against a sterile white background: she is a force.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:720.2956204379558,36.86496350364962,615.8868613138691,530.9343065693431"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/canvas/1/d016ff5e-170f-49a1-834d-1bae12206b0e","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:21:30.599Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The regimentation of Reynolds’ daily life is not limited to Reynolds himself. Even Cyril, although a dominating force herself, is held to his expectations and routines, as we can see in her placement between the window shutters.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-00208/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:541.7189781021899,597.9197080291967,1185.1313868613136,437.7043795620442"}}}]}]}]}